SUMMARY:Mixed Chair/Standing Exercises
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register on 
 the Adult School website.\n\nIf you have difficulty doing exercises on the 
 floor\, this is the class for you. Learn movements while standing and 
 sitting in a chair. The result will be greater strength\, toning and 
 flexibility\, and may help to improve balance. Light weights or therabands 
 are optional.
LOCATION:Montclair - First Lutheran Church\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Fitness
