SUMMARY:Gentle Yoga for Welllness
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nGentle and simple yoga poses designed to help release 
 tension\, enhance energy\, stretch and strengthen the body\, relax the mind 
 and lift the spirits. Class begins with brief warm-ups seated in a chair 
 and then transitions to standing and balance work followed by poses done 
 while reclined on the floor. It is safe for students with osteoporosis.\n
LOCATION:Montclair - Cornerstone Montclair\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Fitness, Health & Wellness
UID:LibCal-10306-15787771
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/15787771
END:VEVENT
