SUMMARY:Raising Readers (birth to 5 years old)
DESCRIPTION:Join us in activities to raise up lifelong readers! We’ll be 
 hearing stories\, singing songs and setting a strong foundation for 
 literacy skills. Exposing young children to read-alouds\, songs\, rhymes 
 and chants is an important stepping stone in becoming a reader. We will be 
 exploring a new theme each week. \n\n\nNo registration required\; space is 
 limited. Please choose the 10:30 OR 11:15 session.
