SUMMARY:MWC Presents: Thriving with Confidence in Menopause and Beyond with Suzi Dia of Montclair Health Coaching
DESCRIPTION:Local health professional and Certified Health and Wellness Coach\, Suzi Dia of Montclair Health Coaching\, will present an informative and fun-filled workshop exploring many relevant topics to women as we age. Topics will include sleep\, bone health\, strength\, exercise\, nutrition\, weight gain/loss\, stress management and mindfulness. Join us to gain understanding and practical strategies\, as your questions get answered in this supportive environment. All our events are open to everyone\, MWC members are free\, non-members $10\, stay for refreshments. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/mwc-presents-thriving-with-confidence-in-menopause-and-beyond-with-suzi-dia-of-montclair-health-coaching/
