SUMMARY:Inner Body Meditation
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\n"Awareness of the inner body takes you bey
 ond the mind." - Eckhart Tolle\n\nIn this mediation session we will bring 
 our attention here: to the inner body. Sessions are suitable for newcomers
 \, those experienced in Tolle's teachings and anyone wishing to remain com
 pletely anonymous. They will last around 20 minutes and cameras and microp
 hones will be disabled.\n\n(Depending on the situation\, a free discussion
  may be held at the end with mics and cameras allowed.)\n\nSee you there!\
 n\nEmrys also organises a free Work of Byron Katie online mediation group.
  Visit [this Meetup Group link](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/) 
 for more information.
