DTSTAMP:20260304T214105
CREATED:20260115T194010Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260115T194010Z
UID:10136543-1772877600-1772881200@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:Creative Coding Foundations (Early Elementary)
DESCRIPTION:Creative Coding Foundations is a hands-on introduction to coding for kindergarten through 2nd grade\, designed specifically for early readers and developing learners. \nThese drop-in friendly workshops follow a consistent\, kid-friendly structure to help young learners feel confident and successful: \n• Concept: a short\, interactive introduction to one simple coding idea\n• Practice: guided exploration using visual\, beginner-friendly tools\n• Open Build: time to create\, experiment\, and try ideas independently with instructor support \nEvery session also includes age-appropriate lessons on digital citizenship and online safety\, helping kids learn how to be thoughtful\, safe\, and responsible technology users from the start. \nThe focus is on curiosity\, creativity\, and building confidence with technology—no prior coding experience required. \nDetails:\n• Short\, hands-on workshop\n• Small-group format\n• Drop-in friendly\n• Designed for early elementary learners\n• No prior coding experience required \nCommunity Sponsorship:\n20% of seats are reserved for community sponsorship. Families interested in sponsored spots can email info@kineticmindscreative.com\n. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/creative-coding-foundations-early-elementary/2026-03-07/
LOCATION:RecRoom\, 1 Lackawanna Plaza\, Ste. 6\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Kids & Families
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Creative-Coding-Foundations-1.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Kinetic Minds":MAILTO:info@kineticmindscreative.com
END:VEVENT
