SUMMARY:Wisdom Walkshops (Zoom)
DESCRIPTION:Street Wisdom Walkshops were created by Dr. Marcia McFee\, creator of “The Way” Lenten series.  The WalkShops take place on ZOOM and are facilitated by Dr. McFee as a “way of wandering\, meandering\, and keeping our eyes open for clues to help us reflect and discern about next steps.”  These WalkShops are open to those who want to walk outside or those who want to take part from the comfort of their home.  Saturdays In Lent through March 28. \n  \nFor more information: worshipdesignstudio.com/walkshops \nZOOM Link
