SUMMARY:3D Origami Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Take your folding skills to the next dimension! Unlike traditional origami\, 3D origami (also known as Golden Venture folding) involves assembling many small\, interlocking “units” to create sturdy\, intricate sculptures. Our instructor will walk you through step by step to help you enjoy this deeply rewarding blend of paper folding and 3D puzzle building. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
