SUMMARY:Creative Art Journaling
DESCRIPTION:Starting your own art journal is a great way to capture 
 memories and express yourself. There are so many different ways to keep an 
 art journal. Want to learn all about them and make your own? Collage artist 
 and lifelong journal devotee Kara will help you start your own art journal 
 using paper\, stickers\, magazines\, and more.\n\nJournals and all art 
 materials will be provided!\n\nSpace is limited\, registration 
 required.\n\nKara's YouTube: 
 https://www.youtube.com/@kara.paper.artist\nKara's Instagram: 
 https://www.instagram.com/kara.paper.art
