SUMMARY:Youth Led Second Hour: Pierce Switzer (Assembly Room)
DESCRIPTION:Join us after worship\, as 10th-grander Pierce Switzer will screen and discuss the mindset and piece that won them Best Documentary Short Grand Prize at the 2025 Montclair Film Festival. It’s a topic teaser around local legacies of Passaic River pollution and remediation\, and what accountability looks like today–topics that Union has long engaged with. Come\, support our youth and build conditions for action.
