SUMMARY:Glen Ridge Community Concert: Cavatina String Quartet
DESCRIPTION:Come in from the cold and enjoy the dulcet tones of the talented members of the Cavatina String Quartet\, Sunday\, March 8 at 3 pm at Glen Ridge Congregational Church. They’ll play an eclectic mix of gorgeous music to warm your heart on a wintery afternoon! Learn more at www.glenridgeconcerts.org. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
