SUMMARY:Supervised Mah Jongg Open Play - Monday Evening NEW
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nLearn valuable tips and tricks for Mah Jongg from a coach who 
 will be onsite to guide you and answer questions. Bring your own card. Sets 
 will be provided for this session. No formal instruction is 
 provided.\n\nStudents must know the basics of mah jongg.  If you're new to 
 the game\, or don't feel comfortable sitting at a table and playing with 
