SUMMARY:Graphic Novel Book Club (18 )
DESCRIPTION:Love GRAPHIC NOVELS or interested in learning more?\n\nJoin us 
 for our ......... \n\nGraphic Novel Book Club!(18 )\n\n\nWe'll explore a 
 new graphic novel every month to read together and then meet to discuss the 
 book.\n\nThis book club is exclusive for those 18 or older\, as some 
 materials may contain content not suitable for younger audiences.\n\n\nThis 
 month's read: \n\nSimplicity: A Novel by Mattie Lubchansky\n\nCopies of the 
 book will be available to pick up at the BAB Library. Check Hoopla and 
 Libby for digital copies!\n\nRegistration is required.\n
LOCATION:Montclair Bellevue Ave Branch - First Floor\, Montclair Bellevue Avenue Branch
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Bellevue Avenue Branch":MAILTO:branch-events@montclairlibrary.org
