 mmers who are a little more comfortable in the water but still want to im
 prove their technique and expand what skills they know. \n \nSkills Focus
 :\n\nSwimming unassisted on your front and back \nImprove treading (in th
 e deep end)\nImproving breath control in the water\nLearn alternate kicks
  (Dolphin Kick)\nIntroduction to and/or improving your breaststroke\nSwim
 ming laps\nIntroduction to open and flip turns\nIntroduction to Butterfly
 \n\nHow do I Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a valid 
 Montclair State ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nWednesday: 5-6PM\nStudent Recrea
 tion Center - Pool \n\n\n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional I
 nformation can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event
 /11940187
