DESCRIPTION:Do You have a huge Pokémon fan? Is your child starting to ask 
 about manga and anime? Maybe you’re just curious about the hype around 
 manga and anime.\n\nWell this workshop is for you!\n\nJoin us as we explore 
 the different genres within anime/manga\, how manga is beneficial to 
 readers\, and how to navigate the growing landscape that is manga!
