SUMMARY:911 Series: Flight 93 Memorial Back Roads and Rail Beds Hike
DESCRIPTION:Metrotrails: NJ\, PA\, NY Metropolitan Area Hiking and More!\n
 Join us for this point to point two days of hiking between Hooversville an
 d Garrett\, 16 miles one day and 17 the other.\nThis finally brings us to 
 the Flight 93 Memorial after years of hiking the 911 Memorial Trail and co
 nnections.\nThe route includes back roads\, rail trails\, regular trail\, 
 and rail trail. Should be easy walking overall.\nBecause there is nothing 
 directly on the route\, those doing both days can shuttle with us 9 miles 
 west to the town of Somerset where we will have hotel rooms.\nIf needed\, 
 contact me at 9083438374
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/metrotrails/events/311535374/
