 ready to pivot into something new\, our flexible\, career-focused curricu
 lum will help you build the skills\, confidence\, and connections to make
  it happen. Registration is open for our virtual information session Marc
 h 18 at 9:30 AM (EST). Join us to explore our MBA pathways and find the o
 ne that aligns with your goals.\n\nHosted by: The Office of Graduate Admi
 ssions\n\nOnline Location: https://graduate.montclair.edu/register/?id=4b
 641c6d-7647-4c92-813e-2c7d04fc05d3\n\nAdditional Information can be found
