DESCRIPTION:This workshop is designed for students who wish to deepen thei
 r understanding of the use of the past tense and imperfect tense in story
 telling. Through clear explanations\, contextualized examples\, and pract
 ical activities\, we will analyze the differences between completed actio
 ns and habitual or ongoing actions in the past. Participants will learn t
 o identify when to use each tense to improve clarity\, accuracy\, and flu
 ency in their written and oral storytelling.\n\nHosted by: Center for Lat
 ino Heritage & Spanish Language Excellence\n\nOnline Location: https://mo
 ntclair.zoom.us/j/91959315458\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: 
