UID:TU2042067998
DTSTAMP:20260303T200314Z
SUMMARY:Interfaith Community Conversation
DESCRIPTION:Join Rabbi Julie and President Aaron Delaney in a series of dis
 cussions around the Interfaith Community.\n\nRabbi Julie will be hosting a
  series of three community meetings in February and March\, where she will
  present background information about interfaith families\, including abou
 t the demographics of our communities and the policies of the Conservative
  Movement on this issue. Participants in these meetings will be invited to
  give input and engage in dialogue with the Rabbi\, Aaron Delaney\, and wi
 th other members of the community as we share perspectives around this top
 ic.\n\nBabysitting will be available at the Sunday sessions upon request (
 email Aviva Arad aarad@shomrei.org).\n\nThe dates of the Community Meeting
 s are as follows:\n\nSunday\, February 22\, 10:00 – 11:30am\n\nTuesday\,
  March 3\, 8:00 – 9:30pm\, Zoom Only (https://shomrei.org/z\\_rabbijulie
 : https://shomrei.org/z_rabbijulie)\n\nSunday\, March 22\, 1:00 – 2:30pm
  at the social hall\n\n
CATEGORIES:Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260322T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260322T143000
CREATED:20260212T183231Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260227T184150Z
