DESCRIPTION:Learn horseback riding basics at the Echo Lakes Stable. We'll 
 go on a gorgeous trail ride through beautiful fields and trails that foll
 ow the path next to mountain sides with swiftly running streams. NOTE: WE
 IGHT LIMIT 225lb\nHow do I sign-up?\n \n\nRegistration opens on Fusion Ma
 rch 1st\nRegister online through Fusion\, in the Student Recreation Cente
 r's main office\, or over the phone (973-655-3340).\nCost for Students $2
 0\n\nWhere and when?\n\nSunday March 22\, 2026\n9:30 a.m. - 2 p.m.\nBegin
 s at Student Recreation Center\n\n \nWhat to bring: Water\, lunch\, long 
 pants\, sneakers/boots and sunscreen.\nPotential Hazards: Unpredictable w
 eather changes\, sunburn/heat exhaustion\, dehydration\, allergic reactio
 ns/poisonous plants\, insect bites and injury by running\, including spra
 ins\, lacerations\, abrasions and fractures\, injuries by animal includin
 g bites\, falls from height and injuries from hooves including kicks and 
 steps.\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Information can be f
 ound at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12179606
DTEND:20260322T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260305T024118Z
DTSTART:20260322T133000Z
LOCATION:Begins at Student Recreation Center
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Horseback Riding Trip
