DESCRIPTION:Turn data into decisions that move your career forwardMontclai
 r’s MS in Business Analytics is built for professionals who are ready to 
 lead with insight\, not just information. This program goes beyond techni
 cal training—it’s about transforming data into strategy and becoming the 
 voice decision-makers trust.This session will also cover the specialized 
 analytics programs we offer:\n\nBusiness Analytics Graduate Certificate\n
 Digital Marketing Analytics (MS)\nHuman Resource Analytics (MS)\n\nJoin u
 s for a virtual information session March 24 at 9:30 AM (EST) and discove
 r how we'll prepare you to lead in this high-growth field.\n\nHosted by: 
 The Office of Graduate Admissions\n\nOnline Location: https://graduate.mo
 ntclair.edu/register/?id=52e18259-2886-45e0-9bb1-5c27f837d50c\n\nAddition
