 ced Labor & Employment group attorneys\, designed to guide employers throu
 gh many essential steps in managing their workforce and ensuring complianc
 e with employment and immigration laws. This event will provide an actiona
 ble checklist to help you stay ahead of regulatory requirements\, prevent 
 legal issues\, and create a healthy\, lawful workplace. ﻿﻿ Whether you
 're a small business owner or managing a large corporation\, this session 
 will equip you with the knowledge and tools to minimize legal risks and fo
 ster a productive\, compliant work environment. Don't miss out on this opp
 ortunity to ensure your company is on the right track with legal best prac
 tices! Space is limited to the first 60 registrants. Register now!
