DESCRIPTION:In this workshop\, learn some practical ways to increase the e
 ffectiveness of your database searches. As databases have become larger\,
  searching has actually become more difficult to do well without knowing 
 more about how these databases are being developed and managed today. We’
 ll discuss using Boolean searching tools to manipulate search results\, h
 ow to engage with database thesauri and a controlled vocabulary\, linked 
 subject headings\, setting up search alerts\, and more.\nRegister Here: h
