DESCRIPTION:Step into the brand-new PLAE Room and discover upLIFT—a judgem
 ent-free program designed to help every student\, from complete beginners
  to seasoned gym-goers\, feel confident and capable with free-weight trai
 ning. Learn proper lifting technique\, get personalized form checks\, and
  master the basics of creating your own effective workout programs. Wheth
 er you’re looking to meet other students who love to lift\, pursue new fi
 tness goals\, or simply feel more at home in the weight room\, upLIFT off
 ers a supportive community and a dedicated space to grow. The program is 
 structured for steady progression throughout the semester\, but you’re we
 lcome to drop in anytime and join at your own pace.\nHow do I sign-up?\n\
 nNo registration required\nFREE for students with a valid Montclair State
  ID\n\nWhere and when?\n\nBeginning February 3\, ending April 23\nTuesday
 s 3 PM - 4 PM\, Wednesdays 6 PM - 7 PM\, and Thursdays 2 PM - 3 PM\nStude
 nt Recreation Center PLAE Room\n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAddit
 ional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engag
 e/event/12179199
