DESCRIPTION:Cru is a caring community passionate about connecting people t
 o Jesus Christ! Join us in learning together on Who Christ is\, building 
 a personal relationship with Him\, and joining a community filled with lo
 ve and open arms! \nThis semester\, we will be focusing on the theme "Ide
 ntity in Christ." We pray that our students will learn more about who the
 y are in Christ\, and look at some examples of people in the Bible where 
 God revealed their true identity in Christ!\n"And they devoted themselves
  to the apostles' teaching and the fellowship\, to the breaking of bread 
 and the prayers. And awe came upon every soul\, and many wonders and sign
 s were being done through the apostles. And all who believed were togethe
 r and had all things in common. And they were selling their possessions a
 nd belongings and distributing the proceeds to all\, as any had need. And
  day by day\, attending the temple together and breaking bread in their h
 omes\, they received their food with glad and generous hearts\, praising 
 God and having favor with all the people. And the Lord added to their num
 ber day by day those who were being saved." - Acts 2:42-47\n\nHosted by: 
 Cru\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campusla
 bs.com/engage/event/12176631
