DESCRIPTION:Come join us in kicking off Asian American\, Native Hawaiian &
  Pacific Islander (AANHPI) Heritage Month at Montclair State University o
 n Wednesday\, April 1 at 12:00 p.m. at the Student Center Flag Poles for 
 a flag raising ceremony.  The Asian Pacific Islander Caucus (APIC) invite
 s you to this ceremony to raise the flag in recognition and honor of the 
 contributions that generations of AAPIs have made to American history\, s
 ociety and culture.\n \nAlso\, enjoy the first ever AAPI "Day" Market on 
 the same day Wednesday\, April 1 from 11:00am to 2:00pm on the Student Ce
 nter Quad. \n \nIf you have any question\, please contact APIC at apic@mo
 ntclair.edu.\n\nHosted by: Asian Pacific Islander Caucus\, Bangladesh Stu
 dent Association \, Korean Culture & Language Association\, Montclair Uni
 fied Filipino American Student Association\, Montclair State University W
 ing Chun Club\, Office of Student Belonging\, The Chinese Heritage & Cult
 ural Society\, Unified Asian American Student Organization\n\nAdditional 
 Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/even
 t/12213737
