DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260418T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260418T150000
SUMMARY:Roller Skating Hang Out - North Jersey
DESCRIPTION:North Jersey Bowling\, Volleyball\, Tennis And More (BVT)\nJoi
 n us for an hour or two of roller skating indoors at the Florham Park Roll
 er Rink\, 192 Ridgedale Ave. No experience is needed. All you have to do i
 s show up! Come anytime. Open skate is tentatively scheduled from 1 p.m. u
 ntil 3 p.m.\n\nThe cost is $16 per person\, unless you happen to have your
  own skates. Then\, it's $10! You walk inside\, pay at the window on your 
 own\, and then you'll see a growing group of people around one of the firs
 t sets of tables likely between 12:50 and 1:20 p.m. Some parking is availa
 ble on site.\n\nIf looking to learn more\, here's the website link for the
  roller rink -> www.myrink.com.\n\n\\*\\*\\* We will likely hang out after
  skating at the Florham Park Diner\, 182 Ridgedale Ave. But feel free to p
 ost ideas below in the comments section. Last time\, we went to a place ca
 lled Recess\, a bar with pool tables\, shuffleboard\, a dart board and vid
 eo games in Parsippany\, thanks to a suggestion from Nigel. \\*\\*\\*\n\nQ
 uestions? Suggestions? Concerns? You can message me on Meetup or WhatsApp\
 , or call/text me at 201-234-9609. Or feel free to comment below.\n\nThis 
 event idea comes to you courtesy of Joe\, one of our many regulars. Hope y
 ou'll consider attending our 7th skating event\, or joining us for a bowli
 ng\, volleyball\, tennis or other event -> www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bow
 ling-soccer-volleyball
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleybal
 l/events/313269115/
