DESCRIPTION:Registration Open NJ Real Estate Broker 90-Hour Basic Broker C
 ourse (Evening/Weekend) May 7th - June 18th T/W/Th/Sat Burgos Realty Acade
 my offers the 90-hour Basic Broker course as part of New Jersey’s requir
 ed 150-hour Broker pre-licensing curriculum. This instructor-led course co
 vers advanced real estate law\, brokerage practices\, contracts\, finance\
 , valuation\, and regulatory requirements essential for broker licensure a
 nd long-term success. The full 150-hour New Jersey Broker pre-licensing re
 quirement includes: 30 Hours – Ethics & Agency 30 Hours – Office Manag
 ement 90 Hours – Basic Broker Courses are taught by a licensed broker-ow
 ner\, real estate instructor\, and ARELLO Certified Distance Education Ins
 tructor. Instruction is designed to prepare students not only to pass the 
 broker exam\, but to operate with confidence\, compliance\, and profession
 al authority in today’s real estate industry.
