SUMMARY:Noontime Cornhole - North Jersey
DESCRIPTION:North Jersey Bowling\, Volleyball\, Tennis And More (BVT)\nThi
 s is an event for two to three hours of casual cornhole at a local park.\n
 \nThe gathering is tentatively scheduled for Lodi Memorial Park\, behind t
 he library\, 1 Memorial Dr.\, because the area has two permanent concrete 
 boards.\n\nThere is not a ton of parking\, but a huge lot across the stree
 t as part of the shopping plaza.\n\nComment below if you have your own boa
 rds and beanbags\, or if you want to bring another yard game. A volleyball
  court and basketball court\, as well as turf field\, are also on site. If
  anyone knows of any other permanent cornhole setups in North Jersey\, fee
 l free to also make that suggestion. We may relocate as a result.\n\n\\*\\
 *\\* After playing\, we'll likely be heading somewhere for a drink and sna
 ck. Feel free to suggest a spot for a post-cornhole hangout. \\*\\*\\*\n\n
 There's no fee to play and nothing else you need to do besides show up. Co
 me anytime!! All are welcome!!! We're not in a league and are not here to 
 analyze your form. We're here for people who haven't played in months\, ma
 ybe years\, and just want to occasionally play and hang out.\n\nThe event 
 comes to you courtesy of prior suggestions for future events and our group
 's WhatsApp chat.\n\nHope you'll join us for our first cornhole event. Que
 stions or comments? You can message Andy on Meetup\, or call/text him at 2
 01-234-9609.\nCheck out bowling\, soccer\, volleyball\, tennis\, skating o
 r one of our other activities at: [www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soc
 cer-volleyball](https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleyb
 all)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleybal
 l/events/313591683/
